Rename a Block - You can rename blocks to provide more user-friendly descriptions of the information they contain.
Available in: both Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
Enhanced Folder Sharing is required.

User permissions needed:

Create and Customize Reports

And Report Builder.

When you add a block to a Joined report, it's named automatically based on the report type and the number of blocks in the report.

Rename a block by clicking next to the current name and enter a new one. Click Save.
